msg: The release has been created from the branch release09.04 (revision 930882) and has been officially voted in the dev list.
The results of the vote have been posted to the dev list on April 13 2010 in a mail with subject "[VOTE] [RESULT] [RELEASE] Apache OFBiz 09.04".
The vote has passed with the following result:
binding +1 votes: 9 (Adrian Crum, Anil Patel, Bruno Busco, Ashish Vijaywargiya, Jacques Le Roux, Adam Heath, Bilgin Ibryam, Jacopo Cappellato, Scott Gray)
non binding +1 votes: 8 (Bob Morley, Marco Risaliti, Erwan de Ferrieres, Bj Freeman, Tim Ruppert, Sam Hamilton, Alex D. Fleming, Ravindra Mandre)
